PrecisAmendments to the NEWFOUNDLAND OFFSHORE AREA PETROLEUM DIVING REGULATIONS which transfer decision-making responsibility on technical and administrative matters related to diving programs and operations from the Canada-Newfoundland Offshore Petroleum Board to the Chief Conservation Officer or the Chief Safety Officer or one of their subordinate officers.

precis:
Amendments to the NEWFOUNDLAND OFFSHORE AREA PETROLEUM DIVING REGULATIONS
which transfer decision-making responsibility on technical and
administrative matters related to diving programs and operations from the
Canada-Newfoundland Offshore Petroleum Board to the Chief Conservation
Officer or the Chief Safety Officer or one of their subordinate officers.
